metadata.name: Peeps Passport
metadata.description: Peeps Club is an NFT collection of diverse & personally curated Peeps characters that live and exist on the Ethereum Blockchain. Periodically, Passports are released for a limited time. This Passport is YOUR ticket to creating your own personalized Peep and joining the club! The Peeps Club NFT you create grants you access to members-only benefits. Visit our website and socials to learn more about Peeps Club. https://peeps.club/
